Package org.phoenixbioinformatics.http

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IRequest
    An API interface for proxy request implementation objects that represent a factory for HttpUriRequest objects to proxy to a target server
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractRequest
    An abstract superclass with shared implementation methods for the individual HTTP method subclasses
    DeleteRequest
    A factory method object that generates an HTTP URI request for a DELETE method request
    GetRequest
    A factory method object that generates an HTTP URI request for a GET method request
    OptionsRequest
    A factory method object that generates an HTTP URI request for an OPTIONS method request
    PostRequest
    A factory method object that generates an HTTP URI request for a POST method request, including any enclosed entity
    PutRequest
    A factory method object that generates an HTTP URI request for a PUT method request, including any enclosed entity
    RequestFactory
    A factory method class that generates an HTTP URI request of an appropriate type given a servlet request, rewritten to proxy to the target server; supports only the following methods: GET POST PUT DELETE OPTIONS
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    RequestFactory.HttpMethod  
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    UnsupportedHttpMethodException
    A checked exception indicating an attempt to proxy an unsupported HTTP method
